<p>Although December is living up to its windy reputation, it's hard to believe we're nearing the solstice. While Steamboat had 90" of snow in November, we've only had about 1.5".</p>
<p>For some reason, I've been reading about Alaskan climbing adventures and watching Dick Proenneke carve his wooden masterpieces once again. I think I really need a snowstorm.</p>
<p>Have a great weekend, everyone!</p>